         vocabulary, payload, and emission discipline are committed
         here as the canonical design substrate. M-INC's
         INSTANTIATE step (b) is satisfied by this file's
         existence.]
    next[Step (c) projection: derive an EDN schema file from this
         flexiarg as needed by XTDB validators
         (`state/<spawned|refined|...>` as a keyword schema, the
         payload as a `clojure.spec`/`malli` schema, etc.). The
         flexiarg remains authoritative; EDN is procedural
         adaptation. War-machine vocabulary EDNs
         (`futon5a/data/war-machine-*-vocabulary.edn`) are
         structural references for the EDN form.]
